\par ____________, 20__ 
\par 
\par ____________________________
\par ____________________________
\par ____________________________
\par 
\par Attention: _________________
\par 
\par Dear __________:
\par 
\par We retain your law offices to represent us in regard to a claim against _____________________, related to ______________________.
\par 
\par Your fee shall be contingent on collection from the responsible parties, and shall be as follows: 
\par 
\par _____ per cent for recovery before suit 
\par _____ per cent for recovery after suit is instituted 
\par _____ per cent for recovery if an appeal is required 
\par 
\par Out of pocket costs reasonably expended and with prior approval of us will be deducted from settlement. 
\par 
\par If not funds are collected, then we are not responsible for any costs, including your firm\rquote s out of pocket expenses.
\par 
\par If this arrangement is acceptable, please sign and return a copy of this letter to us. 
\par 
\par 
\par Best regards, 
\par 
\par 
\par __________________________________________
\par Plaintiff
\par 
\par 
\par Accepted: _________________________________ 
