you in its preparation.  Contingency law suits benefit both the plaintiff, by only having them pay if they win, and lawyers, by giving them a big potential payday
 should they win.  If you are the Plaintiff, you should negotiate hard to get the lowest percentages from the lawyer.  Instead of just shopping around for who you like, consider shopping also for the best deal, as you would for any other purchase.  

